yetho noolondril varaindha

snippet.title: #Video | Disco Mein Kisko Nachaogi |Godfather |#Khesari Lal Yadav #Priyanka | New Bhojpuri Song 2025
snippet.description:
"Disco Mein Kisko Nachaogi" is the latest romantic Bhojpuri song of 2025, released under Times Music Bhojpuri from the upcoming movie "Godfather." Sung by the dynamic duo Khesari Lal Yadav and Priyanka Singh, this love track beautifully captures the essence of romance through heartfelt lyrics and soulful melodies. With its catchy composition and visually stunning official video, this Bhojpuri DJ song is quickly becoming a fan favorite across social media and music platforms.

The music video showcases a compelling love story blending traditional Bhojpuri vibes with a modern cinematic touch. Whether you're a fan of Bhojpuri cinema, love songs, or the chart-topping voice of Khesari Lal Yadav, "Disco Mein Kisko Nachaogi" is a must-watch and a must-listen.

snippet.title: Projapati Song | Projapati 2 | Mithun C | Dev | Jeet Gannguli | Avijit Senn | ‚Ä™Bengal Talkies
snippet.description:
Presenting the official video of the ‚ÄúProjpati ‚Äù title track from the much-awaited film Projapati 2.
‚ÄúProjapati Song‚Äù is a high-octane Bengali wedding dance anthem packed with celebration, colour, and unstoppable energy. Composed in a Jeet-Ganguly‚Äìstyle festive dance beat.

The lyrics carry the fun, poetic, and rhythmic flavour you‚Äôd expect from a Priyo-Chattopadhyay‚Äìinspired wedding track‚Äîfull of joy, jokes, and pure celebration. Featuring the dynamic screen presence of Dev‚Äôs youthful energy and Mithun Chakraborty‚Äôs iconic swag, the track feels like a grand family celebration turned into a dance explosion.

Kanda Sasti Kavacham is one of the most powerful devotional hymns dedicated to Lord Murugan, written by Sri Devaraya Swamigal. Listening to this divine chant helps remove obstacles, destroy negative energies, bring peace, protection, courage, and spiritual strength.
On the auspicious day of Skanda Sasti, devotees chant this Kavacham to seek the blessings of Lord Murugan and receive divine grace, victory, and positivity in life.

May Lord Subramanya bless your home with good health, prosperity, strength, and success.

üéß For best experience, listen with devotion and headphones.
